        "title": "Why choose emotions?",
        "content": "In Nonviolent Communication (NVC), emotions are the signal lights to our inner 'needs'. When we feel comfortable (like happy, peaceful), it means needs are met; when uncomfortable (like angry, sad), needs are unmet. Identifying emotions accurately helps us clearly see what we truly value."
